<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Re:View - 오답 게시판</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav>
            <a href="/" class="logo">Re:View</a>
            <div class="nav-links">
                <a href="/board">게시판</a>
                <a href="/write">오답작성</a>
                <a href="#">분석</a>
            </div>
        </nav>

        <h1>오답 게시판</h1>

        <div class="notes-list">
            <% if (notes && notes.length > 0) { %>
                <% notes.forEach(note => { %>
                    <div class="card">
                        <span class="tag">
                            <% if (note.reason_id == 1) { %>계산 실수<% } 
                               else if (note.reason_id == 2) { %>해석 오류<% } 
                               else if (note.reason_id == 3) { %>개념 부족<% } 
                               else if (note.reason_id == 4) { %>발상 실패<% } 
                               else { %>기타<% } %>
                        </span>
                        <h3><%= note.title %></h3>
                        <p><%= note.solution.substring(0, 100) %><%= note.solution.length > 100 ? '...' : '' %></p>
                        <div style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 0.8rem; color: #999;">
                            등록일: <%= new Date(note.created_at).toLocaleDateString() %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                <% }); %>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="card" style="text-align: center; padding: 60px;">
                    <p>아직 등록된 오답 노트가 없습니다. 첫 번째 노트를 작성해 보세요!</p>
                    <a href="/write" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-top: 20px;">오답 작성하기</a>
                </div>
            <% } %>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
